a=a_{TT}+a_{NN} = \frac{d^2 s}{dt^2}\vec{T} + \kappa \frac{ds}{dt} 2\vec{N}
a_N=\kappa (ds/dt)
\vec a = (d^2s/dt^2)\vec T(s) + κ (ds/dt)^2 \vec N(s), \tag{0}
